{"tid":2259640,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"60歲2元乘車｜鄭月娥：不存在撤回惟未有時間表　須處理濫用問題","createTime":"2020-10-27T03:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T04:57:21.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"69c1cb63995d16374efd897e7f933777b2ed9d99","tid":2259640,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:44:43.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥年初推出10項民生措施，包括將兩元乘車優惠的合資格申請年齡，由65歲降至60歲。惟近日政界傳出，有行政會議成員認為措施衍生的年度支出達百億元，且沒有經濟效益，政策推行存在極大阻力。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥今早（27日）出席行會前首次開腔回應，指相關顧問研究仍在進行中，不存在撤回或擱置已公布的政策目標，惟目前難以立即敲定時間表，因有許多複雜問題需要處理，包括財政、濫用長者八達通等情況。"},{"pid":"05295a433613d12752c9a7d17186c5efc073d8d7","tid":2259640,"uid":184261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"佢識用八達通？"},{"pid":"91477e783af9a596284e9a397aca3d48ffe86df0","tid":2259640,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"林鄭：幾年後班人65就可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb3aeb5114a4b0546e2c9a68778118fd1c7a26a","tid":2259640,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05295a433613d12752c9a7d17186c5efc073d8d7","tid":2259640,"uid":184261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"佢識用八達通？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"dca5e619ef57449f402b1a9ca2c63358968a56f4","tid":2259640,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:57:39.000Z","msg":"咪推出好過，又多一班廢老爭車搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a146e2dfe94eb67d1eaec838c5966d58a70912","tid":2259640,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"你開左個原意叫敬老， 你理佢點用？ CUT 埋生果金啦笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />